original: Levander, Ingrid Hilma Elisabet, tandläkare. I\oTrköping, f. 19/1/11 i Umeå landsförs. av kommin. Georg L. o. Tekla Ödén. — Studiex. i Umeå 29, tandhkand. 3’2, tandläkare 36. Praktik i Vetlanda 36-47, i Norrköp. sed. 47.
translated: Levander, Ingrid Hilma Elisabet, dentist. Born on January 19, 1911 in Umeå rural parish to the minister Georg L. and Tekla Ödén. — Completed studies in Umeå in 1929, dental degree in 1932, became a dentist in 1936. Practiced in Vetlanda from 1936 to 1947, and in Norrköping since 1947.
